		<div id="comment_body_64173707">Doesn't change the facts. They are the world's largest polluter. The "agreements" they've signed aren't changing the facts on the ground and they've been egregious liars in the past when it comes to multilateral agreements, as have most countries. Political solutions to climate change seem unlikely. Technical solutions have a lot more potential.</div>
